description: Omar is a sophomore in college and is quite the party animal.He told us about some of the wild parties he's been to (and thrown) and some of the crazy things he's done. It's clear he's having a great time living it up. Omar has a very well-toned body, and enjoys keeping it in shape with at least 4-5 trips to the gym every week. Keep up the good work, Omar... it shows.
title: Omar
